     fhir:div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p><b>Generated Narrative: ServiceRequest</b><a name=\"RadiotherapyCoursePrescription-352-634\"> </a></p><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Resource ServiceRequest &quot;RadiotherapyCoursePrescription-352-634&quot; Version &quot;4046788&quot; Updated &quot;2023-08-18 17:09:58+0200&quot; </p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profiles: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/us/codex-radiation-therapy/STU1/StructureDefinition-codexrt-radiotherapy-course-prescription.html\">Radiotherapy Course Prescription</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-RadiotherapyCoursePrescription.html\">Radiotherapy Course Prescription</a></p></div><p><b>Procedure Intent Extension</b>: Radical <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (radiotherapy-therapeutic-intent#Radical)</span></p><p><b>identifier</b>: id: 634 (use: OFFICIAL), id: C1_Both_Breast (use: USUAL)</p><p><b>status</b>: active</p><p><b>intent</b>: original-order</p><p><b>category</b>: Radiation oncology AND/OR radiotherapy <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#108290001)</span></p><p><b>code</b>: Radiotherapy course of treatment (regime/therapy) <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#1217123003)</span></p><p><b>subject</b>: <a href=\"Patient-Patient-352.html\">Patient/Patient-352: Sister-22B, Jane</a> &quot; SISTER-22B&quot;</p><p><b>reasonCode</b>: Malignant neoplasm: breast, unspecified <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.0.0/CodeSystem-icd10.html\">ICD-10</a>#C50.9)</span></p><p><b>reasonReference</b>: <a href=\"Condition/Condition-DX-65100000000000000156-2\">Condition/Condition-DX-65100000000000000156-2: C50.9:Malignant neoplasm: breast, unspecified</a></p><p><b>bodySite</b>: Breast, Left <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (radiotherapy-prescription-site#Breast, Left; <a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#76752008 &quot;Breast structure (body structure)&quot;)</span>, Breast, Right <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (radiotherapy-prescription-site#Breast, Right; <a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#76752008 &quot;Breast structure (body structure)&quot;)</span>, Oesophagus <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (radiotherapy-prescription-site#Oesophagus)</span></p></div>"
